  "texts": [
    "In summary, the proposed MoSLoRA consistently outperforms LoRA in various settings, demonstrating its effectiveness and robustness.",
    "More finegrained ability Moreover, we also visualize the normalized scores on 6 ability dimensions in the MMbench EN/CN test set.",
    "As shown in Figure 5, we can observe that MoSLoRA performs better than LoRA on all abilities for both English and Chinese scenarios, especially the reasoning ability.",
    "Reasoning tasks are typically considered to be more complex and difficult.",
    "Compared to LoRA, MoSLoRA mixes more subspaces and is thus better at more difficult tasks such as logical reasoning."
  ]
